from the word cimarrón.

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:08.507
Cimarrón, I seen that in
English, it call my rooms.

00:17:08.507 --> 00:17:10.715
Was a slave who escaped from
the house was the master

00:17:10.715 --> 00:17:13.944
