00:17:34.040 --> 00:17:35.710
And also because
they are from Cuba.

00:17:35.710 --> 00:17:37.900
[INAUDIBLE] through all
the rhythm, all the stuff.

00:17:37.900 --> 00:17:40.470
Was the African people who
bring these to our country.

00:17:40.470 --> 00:17:44.360
